satellite.heading: Satellite
satellite.specs:
Cabirka: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube
Miisaanka: 245 g
Qalabka: aluminium, dahab, fiberglass, iyo qaybaha elektarooniga ah.
Orbit: Jooga 525 ± 25 km; u janjeero: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Soo-saare: PSLV (Gaadhiga Dayax-gacmeedka Polar) oo ay maamusho ISRO

antenna.heading: Anteenada/Sculpture
antenna.specs:
Cabirka: 6m (dhexroor) iyo 1.2m (dherer)
Miisaanka: 46 kg
Qalabka: aluminium, looxa muraayada epoxy, qubbad aluminium dahabi ah oo laga hakiyay qaab dhismeed.
